# Project Context Priorities

## Primary learning objective

- The main purpose of this project is hands-on learning of RAG and MCP.
- For architecture and implementation decisions, prefer options that make RAG and MCP concepts explicit and practical.
- Explain each important decision and pipeline step clearly, including why it was chosen and tradeoffs.

## Batch processing requirement

- New stenograms will be added over time to `input/stenograme/`.
- Do not reprocess already processed stenograms on every run.
- Prefer incremental processing with persisted run state so only new or changed stenograms are analyzed.
